desc_short	-----								From the people who brought you Sins of a Solar Empire comes a new massive real-time strategy game, Ashes of the Singularity. Take command of an interstellar empire as you battle across the surface of entire worlds.							
developer									Oxide Games					,			Stardock Entertainment								
